<item>
            <title>[TIKA-282] RTF parser expects a GUI environment</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-282</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As reported in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-2329&quot; title=&quot;Build fails on system without X&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JCR-2329&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;JCR-2329&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the RTF parser in Tika fails with an InternalError when run in a Unix environment without an X11 server:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  java.lang.InternalError: Can&apos;t connect to X11 window server using &apos;:0.0&apos; as the value of the DISPLAY variable.&lt;br/&gt;
